OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,7,FSarah Corker explains how new ADHD
OL,8,Ftests could speed up diagnoses.
OL,10,FAn online test which could help
OL,11,Fdiagnose children and young people
OL,12,Fwith Attention Deficit Hyperactivity
OL,13,FDisorder (ADHD) faster has been
OL,14,Frecommended for use on the NHS.
OL,16,FKnown as the QbTest, the computer-
OL,17,Fbased assessment tracks the movements
OL,18,Fof patients while measuring the three
OL,19,Fmain symptoms of ADHD, which are
OL,20,Finattention, impulsivity, and
OL,21,Fhyperactivity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
