OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FResults are then compared with
OL,7,Fpatients of the same age who do not
OL,8,Fhave ADHD.
OL,10,FIn draft guidance, the National
OL,11,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,12,FExcellence (Nice) has recommended
OL,13,FQbTest be used by the NHS to aid the
OL,14,Fdiagnosis of patients aged six to 17
OL,15,Falongside standard clinical assessment.
OL,17,FEvidence from trials suggests it could
OL,18,Fincrease the number of young patients
OL,19,Fbeing diagnosed, or having the
OL,20,Fcondition ruled out, within six months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
