OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FAt the moment, children and young
OL,7,Fpeople suspected of having ADHD have
OL,8,Fthe condition diagnosed or ruled out
OL,9,Ffollowing a detailed assessment.
OL,11,FThis can include interviews with the
OL,12,Fchild, their parents or teachers, as
OL,13,Fwell as a physical examination to rule
OL,14,Fout other possible causes for the
OL,15,Fsymptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
