OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FMark Chapman, director of Nice's
OL,7,FHealthTech programme, said: "Evidence
OL,8,Fpresented to our committee showed the
OL,9,FQbTest could increase the number of
OL,10,Fchildren and young people who get a
OL,11,Fdiagnostic decision within six months
OL,12,Fof starting assessment."
OL,14,FThere is currently no national data
OL,15,Fpublished on referrals or waiting
OL,16,Ftimes for ADHD assessments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
