OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FHowever, an online survey by the
OL,7,FPetitions Committee, carried out in
OL,8,F2022, asked people for their view of
OL,9,Fassessment waiting times for ADHD and
OL,10,Fautism, and attracted 7,340 responses.
OL,12,FThe research found that, among
OL,13,Fpatients who had had an ADHD
OL,14,Fdiagnosis, some 27% waited between six
OL,15,Fmonths and one year for an NHS
OL,16,Fassessment, with the same proportion
OL,17,Fwaiting between one and two years and
OL,18,F14% waiting for two to three years.
