OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FMr Chapman said: "Children and young
OL,7,Fpeople with ADHD deserve to receive a
OL,8,Fdiagnosis in a timely manner.
OL,10,F"We heard from our patient experts
OL,11,Fthere are challenges with current
OL,12,Fpathways.
OL,14,F"We're committed to ensuring we get
OL,15,Fthe best care to people fast while
OL,16,Fproviding value for money to the
OL,17,Ftaxpayer. This technology has the
OL,18,Fpotential to generate tangible
OL,19,Fbenefits to the lives of those waiting
OL,20,Ffor an ADHD diagnosis."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
